headline: This Week In AI Chips - TCS and AMD Unite to Boost AI Solutions
summary: Tata Consultancy Services (TCS) and Advanced Micro Devices (AMD) have announced a strategic collaboration aimed at enhancing AI accessibility and adoption across enterprises. This partnership focuses on co-developing industry-specific AI and GenAI solutions, leveraging TCS's systems integration capabilities and AMD’s high-performance computing technologies. The collaboration aims to modernize hybrid cloud and edge environments, deploy AI-powered solutions, and enhance AI performance for...
